1
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:52,679
Today,

2
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,679
I will execute you

3
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:57,560
on the spot

4
00:00:58,119 --> 00:01:00,079
and bring justice

5
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:02,439
to those innocent souls!

6
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,400
Senior Mu,

7
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,319
His Highness is interrogating the demon.

8
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,439
Leave now!

9
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:21,719
Your Highness,

10
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,840
I heard you caught the Dream-Eating Demon.

11
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,000
Where is it now?

12
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:28,360
The Royal Advisor's charms

13
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,240
controlled it for a moment,

14
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,560
but it broke free.

15
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:36,639
I'll send demon hunters to search.

16
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,120
When I return to the temple,

17
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:39,199
I'll tell the master

18
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,319
to revise the talisman and present it to you.

19
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:43,879
Today,

20
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:45,039
I'll take my leave.

21
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:44,240
Shen Que said the demon escaped the talisman?

22
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,319
Yes.

23
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:50,000
I infused the talisman with great power.

24
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,959
The demon couldn't have escaped.

25
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:54,680
It must be His Highness

26
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,199
who released it.

27
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:58,480
His sentimentalism

28
00:04:58,839 --> 00:05:00,360
will ruin my grand plan.

29
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:03,199
Rather than letting him cause more trouble,

30
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:05,399
we should just eliminate him

31
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,439
to prevent future issues.

32
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,720
Master,

33
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,160
he is the esteemed Prince Xian.

34
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,240
This is a grave matter.

35
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,680
Once we start,

36
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,160
there's no turning back.

37
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,480
He wields the Demon Hunt Decree,

38
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,720
yet consorts with demons.

39
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,920
Why not kill him?

40
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,240
Are you now

41
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:25,600
defying my order?

42
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,120
I wouldn't dare.

43
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,240
I'll

44
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,759
handle this right away.

45
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,279
[He had the chance to kill me,]

46
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:25,240
[but why let me go?]

47
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,439
[You're a demon,]

48
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,680
[and you killed my brother.]

49
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,240
[Why did he still believe you?]

50
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,600
[Why did he worry about you?]

51
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,000
[Why did he keep thinking about you?]

52
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,920
Guards!

53
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,920
Your Highness.

54
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:56,720
Bring the remains

55
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,040
of Prince Qi.

56
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:58,639
Yes.

57
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,079
Your Highness,

58
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:05,040
here are all the remains of Prince Qi.

59
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,279
Leave.

60
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:07,759
Yes.

61
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:58,079
He built an underground black market

62
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,920
to trade demon skins

63
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,519
for huge profits.

64
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,360
He also conscripted men

65
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,439
and seized homes

66
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,240
in the name of demon hunting.

67
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,600
Over the past eight years,

68
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,480
he has killed nearly 700 innocent people

69
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,000
in the name of

70
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,079
demon hunting.

71
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,839
The list

72
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,480
and related evidence

73
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,600
[are investigating the matter in secret.]

74
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,240
[Be cautious]

75
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:21,800
[in everything you do.]

76
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,079
[Anyone who knows]

77
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,600
[will be killed.]

78
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:32,519
You actually intercepted General Qu's memo?

79
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:36,039
Is this really your handwriting?

80
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:49,360
If the old emperor refuses to abdicate,

81
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,759
take Shen Que as a hostage

82
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:53,720
to force him to abdicate.

83
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,840
If necessary,

84
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,000
you can kill them both.

85
00:08:59,279 --> 00:08:59,879
[Your Highness,]

86
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,440
[you already have the answer in your heart.]

87
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,919
[Only the Utmost Evil One with blood on his hands]

88
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,360
[can devour]

89
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,840
[the nightmares of their victims]

90
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,879
[to cultivate their powers.]

91
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,320
[The perfect brother you admire]

92
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,639
[is not a good person.]

93
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:27,360
[Shen Que,]

94
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,639
[your life is truly a farce.]

95
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,679
[The one you love is the demon you hate.]

96
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:34,399
[The one you miss]

97
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,759
[doesn't even think of you.]

98
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,960
Shen Que has discovered A'Li's true form.

99
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,919
We can't just sit back and wait.

100
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,799
The only thing I hate more than him is the spiritual root within him.

101
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:46,320
It not only prevents me from killing him for A'Li's sake,

102
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,720
but also forces me to constantly

103
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,519
protect his life.

104
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,919
When the spiritual root returns to its rightful place,

105
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,279
that will be the day I tear him apart.

106
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:55,759
Only A'Li can retrieve the spiritual root.

107
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:57,440
We can't push her too hard.

108
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,759
I'm not pushing her.

109
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,080
What do you mean?

110
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,039
The spirit butterflies I sent out reported

111
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:04,919
that the demon hunters are planning to kill Shen Que.

112
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:06,480
Mortal...

113
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,120
They're all selfish and greedy.

114
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,440
How can that be?

115
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,279
If Shen Que dies,

116
00:10:11,279 --> 00:10:12,480
we can't get the Holy Root back.

117
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,960
If we wait for him to be reborn,

118
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,399
it will take another hundred years.

119
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,080
We...

120
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,799
When are they going to do it?

121
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,399
Today.

122
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,559
A'Li,

123
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,879
don't worry. I won't act on impulse.

124
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:29,840
His spiritual root remains unclaimed.

125
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,600
If he dies,

126
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,480
the entire Demon Clan will perish with him.

127
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:34,080
I won't let that happen.

128
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:40,600
Little White,

129
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,159
we must trust A'Li.

130
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,799
She'll handle this.

131
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,279
Go!

132
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,279
Who are you?

133
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:47,399
Who sent you?

134
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:48,879
Take your questions

135
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:49,919
to hell!

136
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:38,840
You're just in time.

137
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:41,240
I'll take you all down today!

138
00:13:00,759 --> 00:13:02,399
I'm the Virtuous Prince.

139
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:05,000
All demon hunters are under my command.

140
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:08,320
Disobedience is punishable by death.

141
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:21,080
I'll draw them away.

142
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:21,960
Go!

143
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,919
Be careful!

144
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:23,879
Go!
